'''Clusterships''' were vessels used to carry [[yammosk]]s for [[Yuuzhan Vong]] war fleets. Clusterships had a full crew of [[Shaper caste|shapers]] to help the yammosk, members of the [[priest caste]] to bless it, and [[Warrior caste|warriors]] to protect it, but it was the yammosk itself that controlled the ship and kept it alive. Because of the special tactical&mdash;and spiritual&mdash;role that the yammosk played, clusterships were heavily guarded vessels, and could retreat from a battle without the warriors stationed aboard being dishonored or [[Shamed Ones|shamed]].

